		{"id":"aa74dca181efc4be","type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241121145907.png]]\n\n给出了变上限积分的关系和值, 考虑使用变上限积分\n$$\nF(x)=\\int^{x}_{a}f(t)dt,G(x) = \\int^{x}_{a}g(t)dt \\implies F(b)=G(b)\n$$\n考察要证明的式\n$$\n\\int^{b}_{a}xdF(x) \\leq \\int^{b}_{a}xdG(x) \\implies \\int^{b}_{a}(G(t)-F(t)) dx \\leq 0\n$$\n由于 $F(x)\\geq G(x) \\implies G(x) \\leq F(x)$. 故得证.","x":-497,"y":1840,"width":957,"height":400},
