		{"id":"c8c9a7aa9e334820","type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241121151408.png]]\n\n设 $F(x)=f(x)-g(x)$. 于是 $F(a)=F(b)=0$. 设 $x_{0}$ 是 $f(x)$ 的最大值点, $x_{1}$ 是 $g(x)$ 的最大值点.\n则\n$$\nF(x_{0})=f(x_{0})-g(x_{0}) >0,F(x_{1})=f(x_{1})-g(x_{1}) < 0\n$$\n由零点定理知 $F(\\xi)=0$. 故 $F''(\\xi)=0$.","x":1360,"y":-137,"width":1040,"height":622},
